-- Erste Group Bank Said to Plan Sale of Covered Bonds
-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 2012-01-31T09:19:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-31/erste-group-bank-said-to-plan-sale-of-covered-bonds.html
Erste Group Bank AG (EBS)  is planning a
sale of covered bonds, according to two people with knowledge of
the sale.  Barclays Capital, Credit Agricole CIB and  UniCredit SpA (UCG)  are
managing the deal with Erste, the people said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Martin at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net  